burlap.mdp.singleagent.model

Class FactoredModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • burlap.mdp.singleagent.model.FactoredModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FullModel, SampleModel, TaskFactoredModel

    public class FactoredModel
extends Object
implements TaskFactoredModel, FullModel
    A FactoredModel is an implementation of a SampleModel or FullModel that computes transitions using a SampleStateModel, RewardFunction and TerminalFunction.
    Author:
    James MacGlashan.
